snippet.title: V: Ghosts in the Deep -- Indie Shmup Alpha Trailer
snippet.description:
V: Ghosts in the Deep, Alpha Trailer -- An adventure shump where you must maneuver carefully to attack and survive!
Try the free demo: https://www.primechaos.com/
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/primechaosgames
Join us on Discord: https://discord.gg/ry9swq5

* 30+ handcrafted levels
* Procedurally generated levels
* Variety of enemies
* Branching overworld map
* Combos, score ratings, medals
* Secret rooms
* Three difficulty levels
